  <name>PostMock</name>
  <summary>Modern API testing tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      PostMock is a modern, cross-platform API testing tool built with Tauri and Vue 3.
      It provides a clean and intuitive interface for testing HTTP APIs.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>HTTP request testing (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH, etc.)</li>
      <li>Collection and folder management</li>
      <li>Environment variables support</li>
      <li>Request history tracking</li>
      <li>Automated testing with assertions</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
      <li>cURL import</li>
      <li>Collection import/export</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
